<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/nationalreview/daily/nr012797.html 204.71.237.87 19970209143647 text/html 6008
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 14:37:32 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 30-Jan-97 01:20:19 GMT
Content-length: 5823
