<P>
<b>Truer Words Were Never Spoken</b><br> 


The Washington Post today editorializes against tax cuts. Clinton's "would give an indiscriminate and costly children's credit to the middle class; we can think of better uses of the money." We'll bet they can.
<P>
Come to think of it, we can think of better ways for the Post to spend its money too.
