<title>May 29, 1996 Press Release</title>

<body>

<font size=-1>

FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE<br>
May 29, 1996<br>
CONTACT: Kristi S. Hamrick -- (202) 393-2100. For Radio: Kristin Hansen.
</font>

<p>

<center><h2>WHO STANDS FOR CHILDREN<br>
AND WHERE DO THEY STAND</h2>

<p>

<h4>Pro-Family Groups to Answer These Questions and more regarding
the Children's Defense Fund &quot;Stand for Children&quot; Rally
scheduled for June 1.

<p>

ATTENTION EDITORS:

<p>

For a pro-family perspective on this march on Washington and
the issues children most struggle with join family advocates:

<p>

When: May 31, 1996 at 9:30 a.m.<br>
Where: National Press Club, First Amendment Room<br>
Who: National Leaders and Ordinary Families,<br>
to be announced.

<p>

For more information, contact the FRC media office.</h4></center>

