<title>NR Extra!</title>
</head>
<body>
<p> 
<center><img src="/nationalreview/images/extra.gif" ALT="NR Extra!"></center>
<br>
<br>

<!-------------------------------------------------------------->
<center><b>February 1, 1997</b></center>
<HR WIDTH=50%>
<P>
<P>
<blockquote>






 <LI>Let's just say that the Democrats can't tell Wright form Huang.
<P>
<LI> "You've got a conservative and/or right-wing presence with really nothing on the other end of the political spectrum," Mrs. Clinton complained recently, "so most of what is left . . . in the mainstream tries to be objective and tries to be thoughtful." We had not realized that <I>NR</I> and its fellows so bestrode the narrow road of journalism, but we will certainly mention it in our next fund appeal.


</blockquote>


<!-------------------------------------------------------------->
<P>
<HR WIDTH=50%>
