<DOCOLDNO>IA032-000669-B021-107</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/nationalreview/extra/013197x.html 204.71.237.87 19970209151647 text/html 1954
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
