<LI> Dick Morris, President Clinton's longtime friend and political advisor, reports on WCBS-TV's <I>Sunday Edition</I> that Mr. Clinton more and more sits in a small room, chomping an unlit cigar and playing solitaire. At last, we know why he's "too busy" to respond to Paula Jones's sexual-harassment suit.
