<DOCHDR>
http://www.atr.org:80/nationalreview/extra/012497x.html 204.71.237.87 19970209151808 text/html 2017
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 15:18:54 GMT
