Ideas for New Hampshire: Better Government Competition Winners
The Josiah Bartlett Center for Public Policy
The winning proposals of the 1995 Better Government Competition, sponsored by the Josiah Bartlett 
Center for Public Policy, are outlined in this book. The competition set out to look for new ideas making 
