<B><font size=3> Reducing the Size and Cost of State Government, 
</FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">by
Bob Williams and Lynn Harsh</FONT>
<p>
<I><font size=3>Evergreen Freedom Foundation</FONT></I>
<P>
Bob Williams. EFFs President and Senior Budget Analyst, and Lynn Harsh, EFFs Executive Director, 
